ww.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-at-the-Grammys.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-at-the-Grammys-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-at-the-Grammys-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-at-the-Grammys-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-at-the-Grammys-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-at-the-Grammys-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>西约克郡制造商亚伯拉罕·穆恩（Abraham Moon＆Sons）的磨坊在得知比利·<a href="/artists/Billie-Eilish">埃里什（Billie Eilish）</a>戴着棒球帽在2025年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美奖</a>上制成的棒球帽后，分享了他们的“完全惊喜”。</p><p>在上周末（2月2日）在洛杉矶举行的第67个格莱美仪式仪式时，这位歌手穿着黄色的运动球衣和一顶带有两个小型联盟旗帜的洛杉矶道奇队帽子，并在侧面面板上绣有“月亮”一词。</p><p>该徽标属于亚伯拉罕·穆恩（Abraham Moon＆Sons），这是英国最后幸存的羊毛厂之一。该公司成立于1837年，并创建了出售给全球领先时尚和室内设计师的布。并非所有使用月亮布的物品都具有其徽标，而是运气好，Eilish的Dodgers帽子都做到了。 </p><figure id="attachment_3834761" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3834761" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3834761" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eillish-and-Finneas-performing.jpg" alt="Finneas和Billie Eilish在第67届格莱美奖颁奖典礼上演出。 （唱片学院的凯文·马祖尔（Kevin Mazur）/盖蒂图像）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eillish-and-Finneas-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eillish-and-Finneas-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eillish-and-Finneas-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eillish-and-Finneas-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eillish-and-Finneas-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eillish-and-Finneas-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3834761" class="wp-caption-text"> Finneas和Billie Eilish在第67届格莱美奖颁奖典礼上演出。 （唱片学院的凯文·马祖尔（Kevin Mazur）/盖蒂图像）</figcaption></figure><p>在谈到这一刻时，Moon的品牌和项目总监Joe McCann告诉<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c897kp2gnzeo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC</em></a> ：“很高兴看到以这种现代方式使用的是传统的布料。”</p><p>他继续说：“这是一个活动的蜂巢，整个办公室一直在嗡嗡作响。这让我们感到惊讶，很高兴看到Billie穿着它。<br /> “当您真正尊重的艺术家和有影响力的人出现以及这样的地方时，这总是很棒，而且令人惊讶。它使世界变得差异，对于像我们这样的公司，您无法取代像Billie穿着产品一样有影响力的人物的力量。”</p><p>麦肯（McCann）也与<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2025/feb/03/over-the-moon-billie-eilish-sports-188-year-old-yorkshire-wool-brand-at-grammys" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》（Guardian）</em></a>开放，并分享了：“我们没有提出任何关注，但当然，我们立即发现了它，就像&#39;哇，真是令人难以置信&#39;。” </p><figure id="attachment_3834762" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3834762" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3834762" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-and-colleagues-at-Grammys.jpg" alt="Sabrina Carpenter，Chappell Roan和Billie Eilish参加了第67届年度格莱美奖。 （唱片学院的凯文·马祖尔（Kevin Mazur）/盖蒂图像）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-and-colleagues-at-Grammys.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-and-colleagues-at-Grammys-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-and-colleagues-at-Grammys-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-and-colleagues-at-Grammys-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-and-colleagues-at-Grammys-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Billie-Eilish-and-colleagues-at-Grammys-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3834762